    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "起源部分强调它有Long history，这个领域其实酝酿很久了。研究现状要拆成两块：On effectiveness效果验证，还有On Automatic creation自动创作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Origins",
        "Long history",
